(11, 1, 'Sample data', '&lt;h1&gt;One click demo data installation!&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Pavilion comes packaged with dummy content data you can enable after theme installation. The sample data option will bring all the content&lt;sup&gt;*&lt;/sup&gt; from the demo website into your store. This will help you to setup your theme and start selling faster!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Products, categories, information pages, menus, sidebars and theme settings will be created for you with a single click. You can choose which of the demo designs to import. For customers with existing stores and content, there is the option to import only the theme design.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;tb_text_str_3&quot;&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;sup&gt;*&lt;/sup&gt;Demo product images will be replaced with those that come with the default OpenCart installation.&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),
