(6, 96, 0, 'Pinko', 'True, it''s stainless steel and has some ribbing for rigidity, maybe that''s a little too strong, but it won''t hold up to a branch striking it before bending it. If the manufacturer had some form of support mounted on the underside for strength, let''s say in 4 to 5 foot lengths, this gutter guard would easily match up with the better guards out in the field.', 3, 1, '2014-06-23 17:21:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7, 85, 0, 'John Doe', 'Mauris et sagittis turpis. Aliquam non consectetur mi, sed rhoncus nulla. Proin interdum nisi id enim porta, sed dictum purus pulvinar.', 5, 0, '2014-06-09 15:21:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8, 67, 0, 'Kate Smith', 'Like a number of a other reviewers I had read that the product was of good quality. My question was how difficult would it be to install. After playing around with the sample I came up with a game plan that I wouldn''t have been comfortable doing with full sized pieces. Basically you end up bending the sample piece by accident until you figure out how it goes in best. After evaluating I ended up ordering the full package.', 1, 1, '2014-06-23 17:21:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(9, 96, 0, 'Pinko', 'Cras varius velit ac fermentum posuere. Fusce ac hendrerit nisi; a posuere odio. Integer dui risus, malesuada in pretium quis; sollicitudin quis ligula posuere.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-03-28 17:37:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(10, 57, 1, 'Aaron Neeson', 'The delivery of the sample was timely so I''m not knocking the vendor, however the product did not seem rugged enough for my needs.\r\n\r\nThe product I received is 5.25&quot; high (north-south direction) x 6&quot; gutter run length (same direction as bead of black caulk on side that faces gutter trough, east-west direction).', 2, 1, '2014-06-23 17:26:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(11, 57, 1, 'John Doe', 'Nullam et justo odio. In tellus enim; commodo in quam a, volutpat viverra lorem. Ut vel velit ullamcorper, sollicitudin tellus et, aliquam ligula. Duis in amet.\r\n', 3, 1, '2014-06-23 17:23:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(12, 90, 6, 'Mirchen', 'Wasn''t sure which size I would need so ordered one 5&quot; and one 7&quot; to make sure before ordering the 25ft kit. For the price, it is worth spending a few dollars to know for sure what is required. Also, gave me a real idea of the construction of the sections and how to install before hand.', 5, 1, '2014-06-23 17:24:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(13, 66, 0, 'Kral Slavi', 'Ut elit nulla, porttitor sed porta a, euismod id nisi? Duis quis hendrerit nunc, ac ultrices mauris. Maecenas at vulputate tellus. Integer pulvinar turpis duis.', 3, 1, '2014-04-29 17:31:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(14, 91, 0, 'Peter Green', 'Don''t waste your time and money with other gutter filters! This stainless steel micro-mesh screen does everything you are looking for. It keeps out everything, including small needles and even asphalt shingle grit. The leaf guard rounded type gutter filter not only doesn''t keep out small leaves and needles, it makes it harder to clean them out once they are in there. The foam type (which I tried first, starts degrading and crumbling after about a year. Plus, squirrels pull it out looking for seeds and small nuts.', 3, 1, '2014-06-23 17:25:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(15, 61, 0, 'Sue Harper', 'I am glad I purchased the sample of the Leafs Out Micro Mesh Gutter System. I was so impressed I purchased 160 feet for my house.', 4, 1, '2014-06-23 17:25:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(16, 81, 0, 'Chris Brown', 'A little purchase before a big one. From everything that I have read, this is a good product. That said, I wanted to judge for myself how strong and how well it works so I ordered a sample.\r\n\r\nOne of my big concerns was whether it could handle a snow load without deflecting or at least much. The ridges give it incredible strength. It will flex but the gutters will come off of...', 3, 1, '2014-06-23 17:25:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(17, 58, 0, 'sdfsdf', 'sdfsdfsdfvvfdvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvvv', 3, 0, '2014-10-23 12:42:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
